{"tid":2450172,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黃世澤(世澤老師)鐵粉genzo哥網戰能力算唔算全面撚打哂全波台所有人？","createTime":"2021-03-17T07:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T10:46:59.000Z","uid":73381,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"675bd4455c784b2da54ada969232d4a80db6a316","tid":2450172,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"佢當年賣旗賣到提早退休 依家日日係屋企上連登同人打網戰同宣傳世澤老師理念<br />\n條撚樣下下搬wiki啲terms出黎然後叫人比證據 最高紀錄762小時唔食飯回post<br />\n我見佢食飯時間都瘋狂秒回tom大哥 講真正常人好難夠條能樣玩 <br />\n我諗諗下都係轉撐gen大哥算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EcakQD5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcakQD5.png&h=868740b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh9UU5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh9UU5M.jpg&h=ab8c7a45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ee340b031e6f2b9a0c1965a081969e28eaa0b7a","tid":2450172,"uid":372210,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"佢肯食飯未？"},{"pid":"557d68b5063d8f54cdcee254f4377ced45317d8f","tid":2450172,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ee340b031e6f2b9a0c1965a081969e28eaa0b7a","tid":2450172,"uid":372210,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"佢肯食飯未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"應該未 我見佢由朝早都依家無間斷回post"},{"pid":"82436dcc85e04674bde185c2aef474d4579411d9","tid":2450172,"uid":334957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:01:40.000Z","msg":"下底係傻傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac6a9f8c46e23a75d89465d081e210ebe4a46d8","tid":2450172,"uid":372210,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"557d68b5063d8f54cdcee254f4377ced45317d8f","tid":2450172,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ee340b031e6f2b9a0c1965a081